{"tid":699531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[投訴之都]上年我開左個post話點解tvb唔搞返美女廚房","createTime":"2018-06-12T15:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T18:09:17.000Z","uid":23451,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1e3acb8edd350ee2ab494ff1c54fde923ba794","tid":699531,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/224631_3732392349f9d87eb8c5baa5afa15784.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F224631_3732392349f9d87eb8c5baa5afa15784.png&h=b8252121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估唔到今年會搞<br />\n唔撚講鄭中基幾正<br />\n<br />\nbob，至少你可以話d師奶大嬸鍾意佢<br />\n口才又ok，轉數快，搞笑呢d就唔講啦好主觀<br />\n<br />\n雪雪雪，唔撚知做乜尻，咁撚多年拍戲咪好囉<br />\n個人太認真又唔好笑<br />\n<br />\n第三個，我諗tvb真係冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/205347/美女廚房-3大安排被批造假-網友勁踩節目浪費食物/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F205347%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF-3%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%8B%81%E8%B8%A9%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E6%B5%AA%E8%B2%BB%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%2F1&d=JQD8j6zJUJvgyHEPV5JzaC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=217571f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/205347/美女廚房-3大安排被批造假-網友勁踩節目浪費食物/1</a><br />\n頭先揾一揾d野黎睇已經好撚柒<br />\n<br />\n十幾年前美女廚房好睇就係因為夠真<br />\nd女係真係on9唔知點煮野<br />\nd主持又好嘉賓又好，口賤同即時反應又真<br />\n個個嘔都係真嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入深切治療部個細路唔撚講啦<br />\n<br />\n係咁咦search過下，<br />\n原來套野已經收到500宗投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先排除環保撚，愛護動物撚，道德塔利班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買咁貴食材俾班垃圾煮都唔係問題<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母呀TVB<br />\n12年後拍同一樣既野<br />\n冇好主持呢d可以理解<br />\n但都俾d誠意啦<br />\n假撚到3歲細路都知係為效果而做<br />\n有咩撚野意思呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n拍撚埋d垃圾俾觀眾睇<br />\n搞衰埋美女廚房呢個集體回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母大台喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7f274cd780938895bbaa1cf13de531678a536a","tid":699531,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"十幾年前果兩套，煮活海鮮都好多時要求女藝人拎左埋去就夠，之後有師傅幫佢地盡量一下整死左隻動物先<br />\n<br />\n而家反而亂尻咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話你冇腦定弱智好"},{"pid":"8962a277c7d11f73fa9e54d78d4ab2672764dcd0","tid":699531,"uid":104218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"龜頭bob<br />\n我入黎係屌柒你的<br />\n你真係好撚黑人憎 仲要勁核突<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af60d89066502681f0e1d0a121e50b768f149f6","tid":699531,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8962a277c7d11f73fa9e54d78d4ab2672764dcd0","tid":699531,"uid":104218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"龜頭bob<br />\n我入黎係屌柒你的<br />\n你真係好撚黑人憎 仲要勁核突<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6d59ef80c91b9e8ca738372d025d53608a62e1","tid":699531,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"劉佩玥真係假撚到仆街，造作得太刻意"},{"pid":"580f46d6eda0b9d55e4fc25ef7a4025b3b9e7de3","tid":699531,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6d59ef80c91b9e8ca738372d025d53608a62e1","tid":699531,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"劉佩玥真係假撚到仆街，造作得太刻意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"都唔撚知邊個諗出黎"},{"pid":"d93e334fdc3174ffcf61d82a580bbf99f796b708","tid":699531,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6d59ef80c91b9e8ca738372d025d53608a62e1","tid":699531,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"劉佩玥真係假撚到仆街，造作得太刻意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"年前佢明明做過某節目嘉賓自己煮過嘢食，突然間唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}